name: AcuteMyocardialInfarctionAdditionalSNOMEDCTCodes
title: Acute Myocardial Infarction additional SNOMED CT codes
description:
This value set represents additional codes in the 2018 WI_IVD_CodingDocument_v2.0 for Acute Myocardial Infarction that are not in the value set for CMS164v6.  There is a discrepancy in the last digits of each code:
15713081000119100 should be 15713081000119108
and 15713121000119100 should be 15713121000119105
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Acute myodardial infarction),(Data Element Scope: SNOMED CT codes),(Inclusion Criteria: This value set represents only those additional codes in the 2018 WI_IVD_CodingDocument_v2.0 for Acute Myocardial Infarction that are not in the value set for CMS164v6.),(Exclusion Criteria: Codes present in CMS164v6 value set are not to be included.)
